      "content": "oh okay good to hear. i was kinda nervous about calling the surgeon again because it's a hassle. so as long as i keep doing the warm compresses and the ointment, i don't really need to bother with an appointment or anything right? like it’ll definitely clear up on its own if i just treat it at home?",
